# Buy Smart Lights in India at an Affordable Price - IKEA
## Introduction to Smart Lighting
The aura of your home is easily determined by the lighting setup. A generous amount of brightness, not too harsh, nor too dim, can create a calming effect. IKEA’s range of smart lighting lasts much longer than traditional light bulbs. They are also sustainable in the sense that they consume way less energy than your regular bulbs.

## Benefits of Smart Lighting
* Control this lighting with a finger’s touch
* Connected to each other and adjusted with remote control and IKEA home app
* No longer have to get up from your couch or bed to switch off the lights
* Integrated lighting looks elegant and blends with the background
* Enhances the decor with its subtle yet useful features

